data.description: Welcome Home! Don't miss the opportunity to own this one-level home in "Stratton Meadows" This 3 bedroom home has been updated and has in the past three years had a New roof, Exterior paint, New windows, New breaker box, New water heater, Fully remodeled bathroom, and kitchen! Enjoy the wood-burning fireplace on a cold night. This home sits on a larger lot with two sheds and a sunroom. Walk outside to fruit trees including an apple, plum, and apricot tree.
